27\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33679,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/umar-weeps-for-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":5774,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Umar weeps at the poverty of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: I entered the room of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while he was lying on his side over a mat. I sat down as he drew up his lower garment and he was not wearing anything else. The mat had left\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2780,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/05\/janazah-prophet-najashi-negus\/","url_meta":{"origin":5774,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Najashi: The Prophet prays funeral prayer for King of Abyssinia","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, told us about the Negus, the ruler of Abyssinia, on the day he died. The Prophet said to us, \u201cSeek forgiveness for your brother.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1263, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 951 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20557,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/04\/10\/what-if-dunya-given-to-you\/","url_meta":{"origin":5774,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: What if the world is given to you?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf the treasures of Persia and Rome were opened for you, what kind of people will you be?\u201d Abdur Rahman ibn Awf said, \u201cWe will be as Allah has ordered us.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cPerhaps\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37529,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/15\/4-takbeer-salat-janazah\/","url_meta":{"origin":5774,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Janazah: Four takbirat in the funeral prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 15, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings upon him, announced the news to people on the day the Negus died. The Prophet went out with them to the place of prayer, they stood in rows, and he exalted Allah with four exaltations. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1333, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41279,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/hiraql-rejects-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":5774,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Heraclius: Roman emperor rejects Islam, fearing his army","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWho will depart with this letter of mine to Caesar and thus he will have Paradise?\u201d A man among the people said, \u201cEven if I am not killed?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven if you are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5774","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5774"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5774\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5774"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=5774"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=5774"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","t